
TY  - JOUR
T1  - Impact of Media Ownership on News Coverage
AU  - Kedia, Simi
AU  - Kim, Gunchang
Y1  - 2023/10/25
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2024/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2022.00653
